    <statement>
        
                <p>
                    The board of trustees at the Da Vinci Institute consists of 6 people. During the spring, a delegation of 2 trustees will be assigned to an outreach committee. How many such delegations are possible?
                </p>
        
        
        <p>

        </p>
        <p>
        Show all of your steps, specify which formula you used, and state why you used it.
        </p>
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p> We are selecting 2 from a total of 6 possibilities (without repeats), and the order of the selections does not matter. There are <m>_{6}C_{2}</m> <m> = 15</m> possibilities.</p>
    </answer>
